  "notes": "Digital environmental controller (US 120V/60Hz, NEMA 5-15). No CO2 sensing or control. 4th outlet is a programmable cycle timer for repeated on/off cycles within a 24-hour period. Three digital screens: temperature, relative humidity, cycle timer countdown. Day/night setpoints for temp and humidity via photocell. LED indicators for active modes and errors. Built-in data logger (min/max temp and humidity). All outlet ports have heavy-duty protective covers. Compatible with optional power expanders APCL4X (4-outlet) and APCL8X (8-outlet). Amazon.com ASIN: B07MCW9TRK. 2-year warranty. ETL listed."
